[29/08/2018 12:48:29] <font color="#ffffff">Trae.</font>
[29/08/2018 12:48:50] <font color="#ffffff">¡Ah...!</font>
[29/08/2018 12:48:54] <font color="#ffffff">¡Ah!</font>
[29/08/2018 12:48:59] <font color="#ffffff">¡Irnos, éste casca!</font>
